        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Clean Water SRF Parity Act</b></p> <p>This bill expands the state revolving fund established under the Clean Water Act, including by allowing low-interest loans to be given to privately owned treatment works to address wastewater. Currently, loans are given to wastewater systems that are publicly owned.</p>]]>
        </text>
